Bug report:
${task}

Locate the defect: reproduce it from the code if possible (read-only), identify the faulty file(s)/symbol(s), and produce the plan JSON. Put the reproduction reasoning in "summary" and the defect location(s) in "change_surface".

Bug report:
${task}

Upstream (localization, and verifier feedback if this is a fix pass):
${upstream}

Patch the defect minimally. If the upstream contains verifier must_fix items, address exactly those. Produce the JSON report.

Bug report:
${task}

Patch report:
${upstream}

Verify the bug is fixed AND no regression was introduced (run tests via bash when available). Produce the verdict JSON.
